<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>RED Digital Cinem</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: 'Lucida Grande',Geneva,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #FFF; background:#000;" >
    <!-- div#wrapper begin -->
    <div id="wrapper" style="width:96%;margin:0 auto;min-width:650px;">
      <!-- #header begin -->
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000" background="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head02.png">
        <tr background="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head02.png">
          <td align='left'><img src="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head01.png" alt='' /> </td>
          <td align='right'><img src="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head03.png" alt='' /> </td>
        </tr>
      </table><!-- #header end -->
      <!-- div#content begin -->
      <div id="content" style="padding: 10px;" >
        <h3><%= "#{@queue.name} -" %></h3>
        <p>We have made a revision to the Delivery Policy that you were emailed a few days back.  RED has extended the “beta” period until <strong>March 1st, 2008</strong>.  As of <strong>March 1st</strong>, the RED ONE will be considered to be “out of beta” and customers will not have the option to have their camera “held” to wait for additional feature implementation.  Therefore, reservation holders for cameras #1-#500 who have not yet taken delivery of their camera must notify RED by <strong>March 1st</strong> with their intentions.  Please reply to this email or email <a href="mailto:sales@red.com" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">sales@red.com</a>.</p>
        <p>Should you decide by <strong>March 1st</strong> to continue with the delivery of your camera(s), the final payment deadline has been extended to <strong>March 15th</strong>.  If final payment is not received by this time, your deposit will be refunded, order cancelled, and reservation number(s) retired. </p>
        <p>
          <br/>
          -The Red Team<br/>
          <a href="mailto:sales@red.com" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">sales@red.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- div#content end -->
    </div>
    <!-- div#wrapper end -->
  </body>
</html>